<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row gx-4">
        <div class="col-10">
            <h2 class="text-primary">What is happening?</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-1re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder info" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <p class="text-box text-primary h5"><em>Due to recent event such as the Ukraine crisis and COVID-19 prices overall have risen</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-1re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder info" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <p class="text-box text-primary h5"><em>Many businessess went bankrupt which led to an increase in unemployment in the country</em></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-1re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder info" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <p class="text-box text-primary h5"><em>Rising fuel and energy costs have made it that prices have increased dramatically</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-1re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder info" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <p class="text-box text-primary h5">This has resulted in many people finding themselves unable to feed themselves and their families</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row gx-4">
        <div class="col-10">
            <h2 class="text-success">How can I help?</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-2re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder help" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <p class="text-box text-success h5"><em>Make a one time or regular donation to a charity that works with foodbanks </em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-2re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder help" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <p class="text-box text-success h5"><em>Donate food directly to a foodbank's distribution centre or a supermarket</em></p>
        </div>
    </div> 
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-2re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder help" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <p class="text-box text-success h5"><em>Volunteer to work at your local foodbank or hold a fundraiser for your local foodbank or charity</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="~/Images/placeholder-2re.png" class="img-fluid" alt="placeholder help" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
           <p class="text-box text-success h5"><em>Learn more about the current situation concerning rising costs of living and raise awareness</em></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
 
